---
import { SITE } from '../data/site';
const initial = SITE.founder.name.trim().charAt(0).toUpperCase() || 'B';
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal">Who does the work</p>
    <div class="founder reveal" style="--d: 60ms;">
      <div class="id-badge" aria-hidden="true">{initial}</div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600;">
          {SITE.founder.name}
        </h3>
        <p class="mono dim" style="font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 4px 0 14px;">
          {SITE.founder.jobTitle}
        </p>
        <p class="maxw-prose">
          Bimiware is not an agency front. The person you hire is the person who
          rebuilds the SVG, reads the DMARC reports, and confirms the logo in your
          inbox. The work spans email deliverability, authentication and
          compliance, backed by {SITE.projectsCompleted}+ completed logo projects
          and open-source tools you can inspect.
        </p>
        <div class="mono-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/zpamio" rel="me noopener">GitHub &#8599;</a>
          <a href="https://www.fiverr.com/tatlisert" rel="me noopener">Fiverr Pro &#8599;</a>
          <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>Email &#8599;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
